{"version":"NotebookV1","origId":1083584440950679,"name":"10-6 Decision Trees","language":"python","commands":[{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950680,"guid":"fd6171f5-a66c-41f6-9d7f-4f1d1eba6959","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":1.0,"command":"\n%md\n# Decision Trees\n\nIn the previous notebook, you were working with the parametric model, Linear Regression. We could do some more hyperparameter tuning with the linear regression model, but we're going to try tree based methods and see if our performance improves.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"19d6cbd3-cd1a-4bba-ac90-969a6032aedd"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950681,"guid":"155479ad-2ebd-4688-b330-973b0fefbf03","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":2.0,"command":"filePath = \"/databricks-datasets/learning-spark-v2/sf-airbnb/sf-airbnb-clean.parquet\"\nairbnbDF = spark.read.parquet(filePath)\ntrainDF, testDF = airbnbDF.randomSplit([.8, .2], seed=42)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"f63dd318-127a-4d28-8e36-7f502bf131cf"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950682,"guid":"b16b7a5f-c89b-4840-831d-b322a6ce3ca8","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":3.0,"command":"%md\n## How to Handle Categorical Features?\n\nWe saw in the previous notebook that we can use StringIndexer/OneHotEncoderEstimator/VectorAssembler or RFormula.\n\n**However, for decision trees, and in particular, random forests, we should not OHE our variables.**\n\nWhy is that? Well, how the splits are made is different (you can see this when you visualize the tree) and the feature importance scores are not correct.\n\nFor random forests (which we will discuss shortly), the result can change dramatically. So instead of using RFormula, we are going to use just StringIndexer/VectorAssembler.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"a7f83653-4772-4ce3-96ee-ecffe818c853"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950683,"guid":"4e5b7152-4cb8-4b21-90d3-64d7170b9a1c","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":4.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml.feature import StringIndexer\n\ncategoricalCols = [field for (field, dataType) in trainDF.dtypes if dataType == \"string\"]\nindexOutputCols = [x + \"Index\" for x in categoricalCols]\n\nstringIndexer = StringIndexer(inputCols=categoricalCols, outputCols=indexOutputCols, handleInvalid=\"skip\")","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"12a67119-022d-4054-acbb-19f8b432896f"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950684,"guid":"8e7bf4cc-bcc2-4cc9-bb2f-a8b92372b310","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":5.0,"command":"%md\n## VectorAssembler\n\nLet's use the VectorAssembler to combine all of our categorical and numeric inputs [Python](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/python/pyspark.ml.html#pyspark.ml.feature.VectorAssembler)/[Scala](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/scala/#org.apache.spark.ml.feature.VectorAssembler).","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"da7502ec-d198-4c46-9d4e-773262673b18"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950685,"guid":"eb5047ba-0e62-4d34-b467-5d28bdb394b4","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":6.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml.feature import VectorAssembler\n\n# Filter for just numeric columns (and exclude price, our label)\nnumericCols = [field for (field, dataType) in trainDF.dtypes \n               if ((dataType == \"double\") & (field != \"price\"))]\n# Combine output of StringIndexer defined above and numeric columns\nassemblerInputs = indexOutputCols + numericCols\nvecAssembler = VectorAssembler(inputCols=assemblerInputs, outputCol=\"features\")","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"630d516c-9f1b-43ab-9099-a02631cd3a7a"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950686,"guid":"3022e9eb-0cde-4e29-b046-4441997dfd6b","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":7.0,"command":"%md\n## Decision Tree\n\nNow let's build a `DecisionTreeRegressor` with the default hyperparameters [Python](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/python/pyspark.ml.html#pyspark.ml.regression.DecisionTreeRegressor)/[Scala](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/scala/#org.apache.spark.ml.regression.DecisionTreeRegressor).","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"a4d27c7e-7ea5-47f5-ab1d-be30637adb10"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950687,"guid":"d7cce295-dca4-4568-814c-4c6760b28897","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":8.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml.regression import DecisionTreeRegressor\n\ndt = DecisionTreeRegressor(labelCol=\"price\")","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"139cd6c1-1b12-441c-a5a0-5ff88780d184"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950688,"guid":"9475e09c-766b-4956-935c-128c560c49c1","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":9.0,"command":"%md\n## Fit Pipeline","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"c02c49e2-57ff-4fa7-99d3-7c698178e06c"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950689,"guid":"5d13ead1-19bb-4a44-981b-871b1c82deb1","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":10.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml import Pipeline\n\n# Combine stages into pipeline\nstages = [stringIndexer, vecAssembler, dt]\npipeline = Pipeline(stages=stages)\n\n# Uncomment to perform fit\n# pipelineModel = pipeline.fit(trainDF)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"c696a1bc-efd2-42cf-b825-8a3c735f209b"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950690,"guid":"e2a03cf0-8019-4499-859c-b61250102260","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":11.0,"command":"%md\n## maxBins\n\nWhat is this parameter [maxBins](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/python/pyspark.ml.html#pyspark.ml.regression.DecisionTreeRegressor.maxBins)? Let's take a look at the PLANET implementation of distributed decision trees (which Spark uses) and compare it to this paper called [Yggdrasil](https://cs.stanford.edu/~matei/papers/2016/nips_yggdrasil.pdf) by Matei Zaharia and others. This will help explain the `maxBins` parameter.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"7d62d019-22b6-47f4-929c-46fbfe576555"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950691,"guid":"8b138733-d836-48d4-b71a-154c5a08521d","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":12.0,"command":"%md\n\n<img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/DistDecisionTrees.png\" height=500px>","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"e28bd521-c7ab-458b-9703-e0f359e97359"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950692,"guid":"899337a7-f52e-47b4-996a-94ed1b5bf17f","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":13.0,"command":"%md\nIn Spark, data is partitioned by row. So when it needs to make a split, each worker has to compute summary statistics for every feature for  each split point. Then these summary statistics have to be aggregated (via tree reduce) for a split to be made.\n\nThink about it: What if worker 1 had the value `32` but none of the others had it. How could you communicate how good of a split that would be? So, Spark has a maxBins parameter for discretizing continuous variables into buckets, but the number of buckets has to be as large as the number of categorical variables.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"26ff77dc-ed03-4239-83f8-8c158ebd4a5f"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950693,"guid":"ee560bd4-d6f5-4cf1-a017-41d62452b55f","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":14.0,"command":"%md\nLet's go ahead and increase maxBins to `40`.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"b866a823-73fc-4361-b51a-081f0cc5ae61"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950694,"guid":"6d36e6a5-a02b-474c-b947-d26ed5f362cc","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":15.0,"command":"dt.setMaxBins(40)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"1dffeedb-4081-4576-8dc4-e9172fa69446"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950695,"guid":"02623af7-93ff-4467-83a8-c9a2be6876d9","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":16.0,"command":"%md\nTake two.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"ac22285c-077f-49a9-afd7-78c496861700"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950696,"guid":"8969775e-6f3a-4075-847f-ec2e86f26cb3","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":17.0,"command":"pipelineModel = pipeline.fit(trainDF)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"7727097a-458e-4657-b604-1b2470d1a5f8"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950697,"guid":"2cd9a3f3-02e3-46a6-ae39-9d61a95623df","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":18.0,"command":"%md\n## Visualize the Decision Tree","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user"